                     <textLang mainLang="fa">Persian</textLang>
                     <decoNote type="miniature">
                        <locus n="92v"/>The Prophet on Burāḳ ascending the heavens preceded bywho is holding out a flower towards a lion on a cloud. An angel (?) blowing a seven-headed trumpet.</decoNote>
